""SELECT [pro.Comments].[id], [pro.Comments].[content], [pro.Comments].[createDate], [pro.Comments].[productId], [pro.Comments].[status], [pro.Comments].[userId]
FROM [comment] AS [pro.Comments]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT TOP(1) [pro0].[id]
        FROM [product] AS [pro0]
        LEFT JOIN [category] AS [pro.category0] ON [pro0].[categoryId] = [pro.category0].[id]
        WHERE [pro0].[id] = @__id_0
        ORDER BY [pro0].[id]
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [pro.Comments].[productId] = [t0].[id]
ORDER BY [t0].[id]" (0723d8ff)
